Author: Ethersocial
Title: [ANN][PoW][ESN][Listing] Ethersocial -Optimized Solution to Build Online Forum
Body: ESN News!  1. ESN participated in G-STAR 2018 in Korea ESN participated in the global game exhibition, G-STAR 2018, held in Busan Bexco (BEXCO) on November 15-18. This participation was sort of effort to bring games and ESN together based on blockchain technology since the game industry is often pointed out as an industry in which blockchain and cryptocurrency are widely applied in the real world, ESN team has had meetup with various companies related to the game industry, and this is an opportunity to expand the ecosystem of ESN.  2. Interview with ESN founder Woonhee Lee ESN founder, Woonhee Lee, had interview on the Korean game magazine, Hankyung Gametoc, during G-STAR 2018 in Busan. As it is a sort of in-depth interview with ESN founder, Woonhee Lee, it would be interesting for people interested in blockchain and cryptocurrency. The article has been released through both Hankyung Gametoc magazine and Hankyung news. http://news.hankyung.com/article/201811216337v http://m.gametoc.hankyung.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=49918&looketapps=1  3. Development of SmartContact games on ESN wallet It is on the way to develop SmartContact games on ESN wallet to expend and spread ESN wallet app. Since this is the first game to be launched, it would be simple a game, such as a quiz and board game, so everyone can enjoy the game easily. We're trying to provide more user-friendly apps, so please be more interested in. Learn more about ESN wallet https://www.ddengle.com/esn/10280071

Author: hackyminer
Title: [ANN][PoW][ESN][Listing] Ethersocial -Optimized Solution to Build Online Forum
Body: Unofficial translation of ESN Foundation announcement  original post: https://www.ddengle.com/10942539 (written in Korean)  unofficial translation (using papago with some manual fixes by @hackyminer (aka ethminer at discord) —————- X ——————— X ———————- X ————- Ddengle & ESN steering committee inform the official launch of the ESN Foundation.  It's been more than a month since we started working as the official management organization of Dangle community & ESN Foundation, but we're belatedly greeting to the Ddengle community and ESN supporters.  First of all, we'd like to report on the work that has been or going on by the Ddengle & ESN steering committee for the past month or so.  == Ddengle Community ==  1. Take over the whole site from the twin-dad (@Magnalucus at discord) - (site server transferred successfully / trademark transfer, etc. - in progress)  2. divide the work among the steering committee, Division of Business / community operation.  3. Renew existing contracts and sign new contracts as a result of contract subject change - advertising, business place, operation agent, etc.  4. Improving the performance of the website, adding bugfixes, and new features - In progress  5. Strengthening community management  == Ethersocial Network(ESN) segment ==  1. Take over the ESN from Geminis. - transfer all issuance of Genesis alloc. (premine), all remaining 36 million ESN out of 49 million ESN has been transferred.  - donate development servers provided by Geminis for external developers with no charge - Transfer to the ESN Steering committee Office.  2. Improve the Content Incentive System for the Ddengle Site - In Progress  3. 30% ESN discount promotion and ESN proxy driving app. release – all profits will be attributed to the ESN Steering Committee when the @lionsmany committee director transfers his business to the ESN Steering Committee.  4. meet up with external developers. - all ESN foundation committee and community developers @turbobit, @Topmining @Combba and @ethminer, finally have a meaningful meeting offline for the first time.  We will continue to communicate for future ESN developments and will be the mainstay of ESN's strong development.  ESN Foundation steering committee.

Author: Ethersocial
Title: [ANN][PoW][ESN][Listing] Ethersocial -Optimized Solution to Build Online Forum
Body: [Open] ESN Youtube Bounty Program  Here is the new ESN bounty program to upload ESN promotional video on Youtube.  There have been ESN bounty programs related to ESN development so far.  Meanwhile, ESN team and external developers, such as supporters focused on development of ESN and have made various development results of ESN, such as explorers, web wallet, hardware wallet PR, etc.  However, we currently focus on promotion of ESN. It’s pretty important to get interest in ESN from various people all over the world. It should lead to positive effects on trading volume, price growth of ESN in a long term. If you are interested in ESN Youtube bounty program, follow below.  [ESN Youtube Bounty]  There are two parts of this bounty  1.Participation bounty - Everyone who uploads ESN promotional video can get 100 ESN   2.View counts bounty – Participants can get additional ESN (view counts times 0.5) depends on view counts of the video in middle of August. It could be August 17. Example: If a participant upload the ESN promotional video and it has 1,000 view counts in August 17, he or she can get 600 ESN (participation bounty 100 ESN + view counts bounty 500 ESN)   [How to join the bounty program]  1.Make ESN promotional video   2.Upload the video to Youtube with your ESN wallet address as video information   3.Leave your Youtube link on ESN official twitter as a reply of main twit https://twitter.com/ESNfoundation/status/1024160570906296320   4.Bounty will be distributed during fourth week of August

Author: Ethersocial
Title: [ANN][PoW][ESN][Listing] Ethersocial -Optimized Solution to Build Online Forum
Body: [PR completed] ESN can use Trezor wallet There is chain ID in this network, and each network has its own chain ID.  Coins from the hardware wallet such as Trezor and Nano lever S and the Myetherwallet are divided based on chain ID. Trezor had an error with chain ID greater than 255, and coins which have chain ID greater than 255 could not use Trezor.  But this time, a developer aka ethminer working with the ESN development proposed modifications to this part in Trezor github, which was accepted and applied to Trezor.  The ESN can apply to hardware wallets. Thanks to ethminer.  https://github.com/trezor/trezor-mcu/pull/381

Author: Ethersocial
Title: [ANN][PoW][ESN][Listing] Ethersocial -Optimized Solution to Build Online Forum
Body: Woonhee Lee, the founder of ESN, will officially participate in Foresting Hackathon 2018.  Foresting Hackathon 2018 is a blockchain event held by Foresting HQ for two days from July 29 to 30 in Tel Aviv, Israel.  The event will involve 250 blockchain developers from all over the world, and they will solve assignments for two days. At the end of the event, the winner will be decided.  Through this event, Foresting HQ presents its global recruiting and business expansion, and ESN presents technical cooperation with Foresting and global marketing.  https://hackathon.org.il/event/foresting-hackathon/

The aim of this agreement is to successfully apply blockchain technology from Genercrypto to the guest house O2O platform. Through this agreement, Genercrypto and Jienem will focus on developing the technology in a differentiated way rather than a hasty way. It is planning to combine long experience in shared economy from Jienem and ESN Coin from Genercrypto, which already provides various services in real life. Author: Ethersocial
Title: [ANN][PoW][ESN][Listing] Ethersocial -Optimized Solution to Build Online Forum
Body: 1. Ways that make ESN practical to use through partnerships     1) Goal        - We have focused on games and online cartoons which have high profitability and good and easy use of cryptocurrency.        - We have tried to make partnerships with companies which can commercialize services in the actual second quarter of this year        - We have more focused on looking for a company which can use ESN and make actual profitability than name value of a company.     2) Online Cartoon Partnership        - It would be good to have the partnership with major companies, such as Naver or Daum, but we decided to approach it realistically.        - We looked for the online cartoon company because it has many advantages with use of ESN.        - You can use the online cartoon service through ESN with value of $0.46. However, the value of ESN would be interconnected with the online cartoon service after listing on exchanges.    3) P2P Loan Partnership        - The partnership with Korea Funding the 7th biggest P2P loan company in Korea        - It was a strategic partnership that required mutual help. Both cryptocurrencies and P2P loans are highly aggressive investment.        - As Korea Investment itself has also established a community for attracting investment using coins and for unlisted stocks, we continue to conduct technical and marketing consultations.         - Currently, we are working on two things through the partnership.             1)   A mortgage on mining equipment for miners: This is sort of loan products that miners can make liquidity of finance.            2)   We are planning to provide ESN to large investor of P2P loan as prize to increase accessibility of ESN in the real world.            3)   We think that we can implement both of them in May.      4) Games        - We have decided to working on profitable business with HTML5 games because it is pretty hard to directly utilize ESN in app games or application games. Likewise, there is not that many advantage in client PC games because it already has pretty good payment module.        - It could be meaningful now, such as “I’m mining coins through free games.” For instance, users can get ESN through click advertisement. It could seem like mining ESN.        - However, the specific development direction could be changed during development. First, we have been in a partnership with MobyGames a company services HTML5 games on Yahoo Japan. After completion of the development, it will release a game in which coins are mined for the first time.        - We are also planning to develop games directly based on ESN as both companies get high understanding each other.     5) Additional Partnership        - We will provide escrow services for safety of P2P transactions.        - We will also provide APIs for safety of coin transactions.   2.   Additional Information     1) Mining Conference.        - There will be mining conference on June.        - We will provide useful information about mining and look for many participate companies.    2) Listing on Exchanges        - We think that it is very important to secure various users all over the world.        - We are planning to list ESN on both Korean and overseas exchanges. However, we have more focused on listing ESN on overseas exchanges first which has pretty high trading volume.        - There could be faster listing than we expected.        - We are planning to discuss once it is clear, but ESN could be listed through voting system which is provided from exchanges.

Author: Ethersocial
Title: [ANN][PoW][ESN][Listing] Ethersocial -Optimized Solution to Build Online Forum
Body: EtherSocial Network  Ethersocial has been created based on Ethereum source code. It focuses on optimized development of the reward system for online forums and games. Ddengle.com was created at 2013 and has become the biggest online blockchain and mining forum in South Korea. ESN was incubated at this community and began with a discussion about reward system for contents based on text, image and video by community members in the forum. We have a pretty high level of interest in the practical applications of ESN, and we are more committed to direct forum application of ESN and reward system than to ESN development.  Today, thousands of cryptocurrencies have been issued, and hundreds of coins have been listed and traded. However, it is pretty hard to apply these coins to the real life because there are various barriers separated from blockchain. Even if smart contract based on Ethereum was created three years ago and can be used with simple coding, there are still high programmatic barriers.  We have focused on the development of various APIs which can utilize blockchain and practical applications through discussions with members of our forum about these issues. As a result of our effort, ESN has been launched in 2018. There was no ESN ICO, and the purpose of ESN project is practical applications of ESN in the real life. We are planning to make these various practical cases in the future.       The Future of ESN  ESN has been issued already, and there are some ESN miners in South Korea. ESN is not fully completed yet, it is beginning of our project. First of all, we are planning to apply a reward system for our forum advertisements with ESN. In addition, we will support to make the payment systems of online cartoons with ESN during March 2018.  Our team has been composed of exchange and game developers. As mentioned before, we have more focused on the practical development of various APIs, and we are planning to update these APIs by periods. Likewise, these APIs will be applied to online forums and games. It will be steadily updated based on economic analysis and feedback from users. It is not that hard for us to apply these works with our forum, Ddengle.com, the biggest online blockchain forum in Korea.   Technical Notes  Ticker Name : ESN Block Time: ~13.5 sec Block Reward: 5 ESN chainId: 31102 slip-0044/bip44: 31102 - https://github.com/satoshilabs/slips/pull/277 Blockchain explorer https://ethersocial.net/ API node : https://api.esn.gonspool.com/ https://api.esnnode.org/   Distribution  Genesis alloc(Premine): 49,922,490 ESN  1.   Ddengle.com: 13,000,000 ESN       A.   Annually distribute 500,000 ESN to members of Ddengle.com for 10 years: 5,000,000 ESN                i.   Current distribution to members of Ddengle: 92,500 ESN to 1218 members               ii.   Reward for ESN pool operators and development support: 15,900 ESN to 13 members              iii.   It is the reward for activities in the forum not the operating expenses.       B.   Marketing and Partnership (currently hold): 8,000,000 ESN               i.   Sites which makes a direct contract with Ddengle.com              ii.   Online communities or forums in partnership with Ddengle.com             iii.   Just hold for now  2.   ESN Foundation: 36,000,000 ESN       A.   Shareholders and members who participated in ESN development: 8,000,000 ESN       B.   Coin Sale (May 2018): 10,000,000 ESN              i.   Financial distribution plan through ICO in March 2018             ii.   We are planning to use the collection to develop and promote ESN.            iii.   Open MPDex a cryptocurrency exchange based on BTC and ESN in Q3 2018       C.   Long-term holdings: 18,000,000 ESN             i.   Support developments and marketing of ESN in a long term  3.   Alpha and Beta Tester: 922,490 ESN   ESN Mining Status  ESN mining began through the official ESN mining pool, http://pool-asia.ethersocial.org (January 25, 2018). After that, the role of the pool has been reduced steadily, and we strongly encourage external pools. ORIGINAL TOPIC-https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=3008097.0;all  EthereumSocial (ETSC) is a decentralized platform that forked from Ethereum  Decentralized Forum Application Platform Based on Smart Contract  "It is not the strongest of the species that survives, nor the most intelligent that survives. It is the one that is most adaptable to change."  It has been almost a decade since blockchain ecosystem was born, and many new technologies keep emerging. We are presenting our new technologies not to overwhelm and intimidate others, but to look for partners to jointly advance those technologies further and invite you to the forum to discuss the direction we will head for. Originated from a forum, EthereumSocial is a humble pot which holds all the technologies we have.  For FORUM and BLOG, it provides token management tools that are compliant with the standard ERC-20 tokens based on smart contracts and APIs to deliver multiple services. Users can easily develop their own tokens with optimized size and amount and make profit using coins for their forum and blog. Gazua.tv and APIs of new blog-based communities will be constantly available.  COMMUNITY  You can find out ETSC applications through 'http://gazua.tv/', an up and coming crypto-currency community in Korea.      -Get ETSC by signing in     -Get ETSC by earning many recommendations for your posting     -Play a Mini-game with Your ETSC     -Join Events with Your ETSC     -Send your ETSC to a partner community     -Donate your ETSC  Coins for Communities and Game Accounts  ETSC is created based on Ethereum. We have optimized ETSC as community coins leveraging smart applications of Ethereum.  ETSC activates a social network of people, who are participating in a community based on easily available crypto-currencies and can produce coins at the same same  Ethereum Social (aka ETSC) is a community-oriented POW ethereum network.
